{"tid":1833684,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"1988年、1996年及1998年香港訪港旅客統計","createTime":"2020-01-22T04:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T06:06:18.000Z","uid":149978,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"caa15a691f69a860e43fe1725e7d5948472660fe","tid":1833684,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"1988年訪港旅客人數：617萬人<br />\n當中<br />\n美國：74.9萬<br />\n日本：124萬<br />\n台灣：109萬<br />\n中國大陸：68.4萬<br />\n<br />\n（大陸遊客仲少過美國人、台灣人、日本人）<br />\n<br />\n1996年訪港旅客人數：1170萬人<br />\n當中<br />\n美國：75.1萬<br />\n日本：238萬<br />\n台灣：182萬<br />\n中國大陸：231萬<br />\n<br />\n（大陸遊客仍然少過日本人）<br />\n<br />\n1998年訪港旅客人數：957萬人<br />\n當中<br />\n美國：77.3萬<br />\n日本：94.5萬<br />\n台灣：181萬<br />\n中國大陸：259萬<br />\n<br />\n（香港回歸左就真係回歸左，昔日的香港一去不返。香港即時變大陸旅客的天堂）<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：香港統計處<br />\n<a href=\"https://statistics.gov.hk/pub/B7001FD2000XXXXB0100.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FB7001FD2000XXXXB0100.pdf&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmKZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=1cb19879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://statistics.gov.hk/pub/B7001FD2000XXXXB0100.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"3e261976d1de68b99b3a5226d5b6f81f59150e21","tid":1833684,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:18:52.000Z","msg":"網址更正： <a href=\"https://statistics.gov.hk/pub/B70001FD2000XXXXB0100.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FB70001FD2000XXXXB0100.pdf&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmKZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=a9ac2ef4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://statistics.gov.hk/pub/B70001FD2000XXXXB0100.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"ad580f4b8b1104f252f636eeabed1c6f41b1bfdc","tid":1833684,"uid":286309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:32:44.000Z","msg":"日本1998年少左一半遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2010a13cb7153b5680c7dc7d831d32b0f861c816","tid":1833684,"uid":149978,"like"